trans-unit.source: Represents an assembly reference and the namespace imported from that assembly.

This class is used by <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> to provide assembly references and namespaces required for expression compilation.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> class.
Gets or sets the full name of the assembly referenced by this <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>.
The full name of the assembly referenced by this <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>.

Determines whether the specified <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> is equal to the current <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>.
The <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> to compare with the current <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> is equal to the current <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Returns the hash code for the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> instance.
The hash code for the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref> instance.
Gets or sets the imported namespace referenced by this <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>.
The imported namespace referenced by this <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference"></xref>.
